{"tid":2089580,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"講完BNO未 7.1電單車手足要片 (求車cam)","createTime":"2020-07-01T17:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T11:32:54.000Z","uid":137078,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"741814e804610b1f3e2b6494c7902d0e1f262632","tid":2089580,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T17:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/et8htFC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fet8htFC.jpg&h=2a87ee68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國安法立法生效第一天，下午約三時許，一名駕駛著插有旗電單車的人士，於灣仔柯布連道近謝斐道位置發生交通意外<br />\n翻看附近錄影者片段，現求於事發時，在電單車前方的私家車，車牌「FJ243」「UZ4428」「ML3677」提供後方車cam片段以供該手足呈堂。<br />\n如有任何資料和影片，請即聯絡<br />\n6297 3207。<br />\n<br />\n鑒於事態嚴重，有關國安法第一天生效的檢控，請各界該人士不要揣測和製造光環予有關該人士的行為和動機，因為判刑必定考慮社會評論。<br />\n多謝大家，分享該訊息已經是對他最大的幫助和支持。<br />\n<br />\nSource tg 寶寶channel 見到"},{"pid":"155018de6bb8b10bb1fb0224537c2453c5228c9a","tid":2089580,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T17:54:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f05f23c135418b456d9c8b15a877e6e12f030290","tid":2089580,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T17:54:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb876136e3114ad174ab416e20edadc4145bfd1","tid":2089580,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T17:54:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"df7b3d157e14082b034c5786a89df33f980e2eca","tid":2089580,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T17:54:43.000Z","msg":"Share 去 ig Facebook whatever"},{"pid":"0047fe9ebd17b78c5d770f2ca70127a70884a389","tid":2089580,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T17:55:09.000Z","msg":"車牌「FJ243」「UZ4428」「ML3677」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif